<br>
Yakut had an unuausal personality but she was very kind and caring. Being a Former Amazon Queen, a tattoo, on her left shoulder, in Amazon lettering said in the Ancient langauge &quot;Amazon Queen&quot;.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yasoo, Sana. Have you practiced your candle trick or started your garden? All the necessities will arrive momentarily.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yakut looked at Kally. She had never met this one.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yasoo, My Name is Yakut, Amazon Shamaness of Scynthia, Tanais River Valley, Chadesia, Themiscrya, Lesvos, and Ephesus.&quot;<br>
<br>
She was in many other tribes but those were her top six. She extended a hand to Kally, expecting the Amazon Peace hand-shake. A warm smile still on her lips. <p>-:¦:- Yakut -:¦:-<BR>
