<br>
After the handshake, Yakut's hand went around behind her back and clasped the other. Sana had much to learn, the ways Yakut taught her were ones of peace and using love to fight evil. Not war.<br>
<br>
&quot;It's a pleasure to meet you Kally. I hope you do not have grudges against Northern Amazon Shamanesses simply because we follow the Ancients Amazons. I know of many who have this problem with me. I hold nothing against you, any friend of Varia's is a friend of mine.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled and bowed slightly showing her friendship. Yakut was very formal at times. Other times, she could be as relaxed as ever.<br>
<br>
Shamanism was a very serious thing to Yakut. It was more than an art, it was her way of life. <p>-:¦:- Yakut -:¦:-<BR>
