<br>
She looked up at Kally, her eyes sparkling with excitement. &quot;Look, I did it,&quot; she said happily. <p><html> <font face="vivaldi" size="+2" color="#87ceeb"> <center> Sana ~ Escaped Slave </font> </center> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ukally2000uk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kally2000uk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 71<br> <font color=#993300>(5/4/02 7:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/kally101.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Worthy of comapny?</span><hr size=1> I clap my hands together in joy for Sana and step forward,kissing her lightly on the forehead,&quot;Well done Sana,i have every confidence that you will become a great Shamaness and i am very pleased for you.Is there anything else i can help you with?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxxsanainchainsxx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XxSanaInChainsxX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#993300>(5/4/02 2:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/sana.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Eeeee!</span><hr size=1> Sana beamed and nuzzled into Kally. &quot;Can you help plant the garden with us? It's important and I want you to be a part of it,&quot; she said, her eyes shining happily, looking up at Kally. He